 <PERSON> Eileen </PERSON> <PERSON> Putman </PERSON> is a Washington-based reporter for <ORGANIZATION> The </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Associated </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Press </ORGANIZATION> covering the vice presidential candidates.
