<HEAD>Tens of Thousands Join Anti-Government Protest; Rebels Back
Students</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: LEADS with 9 grafs to UPDATE with hundreds of thousands
rallying in Mandalay, details. Pick up 4th pvs, In the. DELETES
