sted 1977</NOTE>
<BYLINE>By GEORGE GARTIES</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>AP Business Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>SANTA MONICA, Calif. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
 A management group's offer to take <ORGANIZATION> Wickes </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Cos. </ORGANIZATION>. Inc. private in a $ 598 million leveraged buyout has brought numerous inquiries from other potential buyers, the company's investment banker said Monday The $ 12-a-share tender offer, made late Sunday by a management group led by <ORGANIZATION> Wickes </ORGANIZATION> Chairman <PERSON> Sanford </PERSON> <PERSON> Sigoloff </PERSON>, included a 60-day wait before the group would begin buying <ORGANIZATION> Wickes </ORGANIZATION> stock to give other bidders a chance to emerge. Numerous potential buyers called Monday, said <PERSON> Michael </PERSON> <PERSON> Tennenbaum </PERSON>, senior managing director at <ORGANIZATION> Bear </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Stearns </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> & </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> amp </ORGANIZATION><ORGANIZATION> ; </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Co. </ORGANIZATION>. <ORGANIZATION> Inc. </ORGANIZATION>, which was retained to advise <ORGANIZATION> Wickes </ORGANIZATION> management on the offer <PERSON> Tennenbaum </PERSON> would n't reveal names, but said some callers were interested in buying the company intact and others sought information on some of its parts. `` Our phones have been ringing off the hook,'' <PERSON> Tennenbaum </PERSON> said. `` People who have a prima facie financial capacity to do this transaction are calling in impressive numbers.'' <ORGANIZATION> Wickes </ORGANIZATION>' stock closed at $ 13.25 a share Monday on the <ORGANIZATION> New </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> York </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Stock </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Exchange </ORGANIZATION>, up $ 3.87 a share from Friday's close. A buyer of <ORGANIZATION> Wickes </ORGANIZATION> would have to assume $ 2.1 billion in debt. The company's main lines of business are industrial products, including auto fabrics and aircraft and missile parts; home improvement and furnishings, including <ORGANIZATION> Wickes </ORGANIZATION> <ORGAN